rows.label: qev086807_MSG0001
rows.name: Is everyone all right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086807_JNK0010
rows.name: Show Off

rows.label: qev086807_SEL0011
rows.name: Flex your muscles and smile.

rows.label: qev086807_JNK0020
rows.name: Worry

rows.label: qev086807_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Celica the same question.

rows.label: qev086807_MSG0002
rows.name: That nothing. Team Tatsu seen worse plenty of times![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086807_MSG0003
rows.name:
What he means is...thanks for worrying about us,
but we're fine.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086807_MSG0004
rows.name:
I'm quite fine, thank you. A few scrapes are nothing
if it means being able to help Rock.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086807_MSG0005
rows.name: But why are you all here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086807_MSG0006
rows.name: Same reason as you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086807_MSG0007
rows.name:
A few scrapes weren't going to stop us
from lending you a hand![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086807_MSG0008
rows.name: Same goes for Rock, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086807_MSG0009
rows.name: So did you find the selenean sage?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086807_MSG0010
rows.name: I did.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086807_MSG0011
rows.name: Then congratulations. That means you passed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086807_MSG0012
rows.name: But only because you helped me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086807_MSG0013
rows.name:
Ahh, that doesn't matter.
BLADEs all work in teams anyway.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086807_MSG0014
rows.name:
Heck, we spend most of our time bailing
other BLADEs out left and right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086807_MSG0015
rows.name: You're a true BLADE now, Celica.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086807_MSG0016
rows.name:
And any who disagree
will face angry and scary wrath of Elma![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086807_MSG0017
rows.name: We should be getting back home.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086807_MSG0018
rows.name: Sounds good.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086807_MSG0019
rows.name: Home...[ST:wait ]
